<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Yes! This is not one of "those" books. He takes Charley with him to avoid being alone on the road. They both make the entire trip, and there is no ref<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Yes! This is not one of "those" books. He takes Charley with him to avoid being alone on the road. They both make the entire trip, and there is no reference to Charley's death.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
