      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1024827-travels-with-charley-in-search-of-america">Quotes from Travels with Char...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
